      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait so you're saying it's fine if i only have one glass? i'm just worried because the person at the pharmacy mentioned something about a \"disulfiram-like reaction\" which sounds pretty serious. is that even a real thing with metronidazole? i don't want to risk getting super sick.",
